rows.label: qst701711_msg0001
rows.name: Grrgh...

rows.label: qst701711_msg0002
rows.name: Enough now.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0003
rows.name:
Look, guys, I appreciate the sentiment,
but I deserve to die at this man's hand.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0004
rows.name:
That is the dumbest thing
I've ever heard.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0005
rows.name:
No. It's just that my death is the
only possible atonement for my sins.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0006
rows.name: Atonement, he says.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0007
rows.name:
Is that why you've been giving
people help without accepting
anything in return?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0008
rows.name: I'm not pretending I think it's enough.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0009
rows.name:
And you think dyin' would be?
You really think that's what my
sister woulda wanted?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0010
rows.name:
Strewth, mate, you don't wanna die
to make amends. You wanna die so
you can stop feeling so guilty!

rows.label: qst701711_msg0012
rows.name:
I don't give a rat's fart whether you
live or die, but pissing on what she
woulda wanted... I can't forgive that.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0013
rows.name:
When you stop feeling sorry for
yourself, come find me and we'll
discuss our strategy.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0014
rows.name: Strategy? For what?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0015
rows.name:
For wiping the Bloody Lobsters out
once and for all, mate! You and me!
This thing won't be done until we do.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0016
qst701711_msg0017
rows.name:
You're off your rocker.
You're... Wait, you're serious?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0018
rows.name: ...Huh? What are you lot doing there?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0019
rows.name: Has brawly-fight ceased?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0020
rows.name:
Morumo very worried, so came as
fast as possible. What happen?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0021
rows.name: Er, it's kind of a lot to explain.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0022
rows.name:
I'm sorry if we caused any concern.
Everything seems to be in order now.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0023
rows.name:
Changing the past, eh?
Easier said than done. In the end, I
wonder if we're all just victims of fate.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0024
rows.name: Tell me, Minochi..

rows.label: qst701711_msg0025
rows.name:
Does that serene outlook have
anything to do with your transformation
into a Man-Eater?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0026
rows.name:
Not like you to be so direct.
Thinking of giving it a go yourself?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0027
rows.name:
I'm merely interested. As one Blade to
another.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0028
rows.name:
Well, drop it. You don't wanna end up
like me - a lousy mongrel.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0029
rows.name: Is that truly how you feel?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0030
rows.name:
You can't claim to speak for everyone.
At least, it must be different when one
goes into it of one's own accord...

rows.label: qst701711_msg0031
rows.name: What are you saying?

rows.label: qst701711_msg0032
rows.name:
If you think of yourself as a mongrel,
that's how people will see you. You
should try looking on the bright side.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0033
rows.name: Always with that positivity, Adel.

rows.label: qst701711_msg0034
rows.name:
If you want things to go well, you
have to visualize it first!

rows.label: qst701711_msg0035
rows.name:
Give me strength...
I swear being around you lot is going
to drive me round the bend.
